    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine. The S54 power plant delivers linear thrust to an 8,000 RPM redline, with the VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G manual gearbox and a mechanical LSD. This example features a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary structural weak point. The suspension utilizes Bilstein B6 dampers and poly-bushed control arms for improved kinematic precision. While displaying honest age-related wear on the exterior, its mechanical integrity is paramount, featuring a cooling system overhaul and recent valve lash adjustment.",
